VibeBox is a desktop front-end for Claude Code, Anthropic's command-line
coding agent. VibeBox is an independent, community project and is not
affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by Anthropic. "Claude" and
"Claude Code" are trademarks of Anthropic. VibeBox launches the user's own
locally installed `claude` binary and never bundles or redistributes it.
